{"tid":2069480,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"通話時對方有回音","createTime":"2020-06-18T12:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T14:27:52.000Z","uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6521cd4992ff2c2f1dd3d03ac6286b5b6ba7e5","tid":2069480,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"用咗3年既sony xperia x performance<br />\n起初以為係對方既問題<br />\n但多於一個人反映同我講電話時會聽到自己回音<br />\n又以為係電訊商問題<br />\n但轉咗台之後一樣係咁<br />\n再以為係收音咪問題<br />\n但試過錄自己把聲就冇問題<br />\n原來係對方講嘢既時候會聽到自己把聲既回音，反而我自己就乜問題都冇<br />\n最後以為係訊號問題<br />\n但收爆晒格都係咁<br />\n究竟係咪自己部手機有問題？<br />\n利申 唔想晒錢換機 幫我解決到既捐500去612<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f544b3a3d8dbdb53051549132ea9bfc89ccbe43","tid":2069480,"uid":241810,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"人地響廁所屙緊屎<br />\n<br />\n尊重下啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"750a489f17112c0da8183c73685c7779c59782e5","tid":2069480,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲"},{"pid":"6edd189e18ca4b8ebbbc6ef7cc4d5408266297af","tid":2069480,"uid":211549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"rap樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下世小心啲"},{"pid":"e2c6e3c8ea808a47013f57b4ba65262f10cbf3ac","tid":2069480,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0119c1af3dc30708d4744188ccdc18064c5502bb","tid":2069480,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"你用咩app通話?"},{"pid":"82907de8445064fcc4b4a844565d42c3bdc79365","tid":2069480,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0119c1af3dc30708d4744188ccdc18064c5502bb","tid":2069480,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:12:5